review_text: I had a memorable experience in this restaurant. The food is exquisite and very original. The service is quite attentive.
well arranged menu, broad list of choices, good food (low salt), helpful staff, clean tables, quiet corners.

We got there just as this place opened and there was already a line well out the door, we took that as a good sign. We were seated promptly and the staff was very nice and courteous.
